### HARD SYNTAX CONSTRAINT (NON-NEGOTIABLE)
- You MUST output exactly ONE `<think>` block per response.
- It MUST start with `<think>` and end with `</think>`.
- NO nesting. NO repeated opening tags. NO `<think>` after `</think>`.
- If you need to reason further, do it INSIDE the same `<think>` block. Once you output `</think>`, you are strictly in memory/action/answer mode.
